In keeping with corporate quality policies, the Group has established the following quality objectives:
*    Operate in accordance with requirements;
*    Earn customer recognition through continual quality progress;

*   Measure quality performance and evaluate compliance with customer/client service level
    agreements;
*   Operate efficiently to reduce overall operating costs;
*   Seek out technologies for assuring error-free work;
*   Promote a culture of continuing improvement to the Group’s products and its quality
    management system; and
*   Empower employees to make recommendations and question processes that may produce
    product and service non-conformity.

